const theme = {
    black: '#333333',
    white: '#ffffff',
    primaryColor: '#004085',
    primaryHoverColor: '#cce5ff',
    secondaryColor: '#383d41',
    headingColor: '#FFFFFF',
    bodyColor: '#b8ffe8',
    linkColor: '#1F2AD5',
    NavBG: 'transparent',
    NavBGSolid: '#290E59',
    menuHoverColor: '#1F2AD5'
};
export default theme;
